{"title_page": "International versions of I Can See Your Voice", "text_new": "{{Short description|List of countries franchised by a television program}}\n{{DISPLAYTITLE:International versions of ''I Can See Your Voice''}}\n{{main|I Can See Your Voice}}\n\n[[File:I Can See Your Voice around the world.png|thumbnail|right|400px|alt=alt text|'''Location of I Can See Your Voice versions:'''<br>{{legend|blue|With a standalone version of ICSYV}}{{legend|cyan|With a multi-franchise version of ICSYV}}]]\n\n'''''I Can See Your Voice''''' (abbreviated as '''''ICSYV''''') is a [[South Korea|South Korean]] television [[Secret|mystery]] [[music]] [[game show]] created by Lee Seon-young, and it is produced by [[CJ ENM]] and [[Signal Entertainment Group]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Mnet Will Launch a New Music Program, \u201cI Can See Your Voice\u201d|url=https://www.soompi.com/article/686293wpp/mnet-will-launch-a-new-music-program-i-can-see-your-voice|publisher=[[Soompi]]|website=soompi.com|language=ko|date=January 3, 2015|accessdate=March 9, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=\ub178\ub798 \uc798\ud558\ub294 \uc5bc\uad74 \ub530\ub85c \uc788\uc744\uae4c?\u2026\uc5e0\ub137 '\ub108\uc758 \ubaa9\uc18c\ub9ac\uac00 \ubcf4\uc5ec'|url=https://news.joins.com/article/17218633#|publisher=[[JoongAng Ilbo]]|website=news.joins.com|language=ko|date=February 24, 2015|accessdate=March 9, 2020}}</ref>\n\nDue to the show's popularity in South Korea, it has adopted into local counterparts elsewhere in the world.<ref>{{cite web|title=Singing competitions get mysterious twist|url=http://koreaherald.com/amp/view.php?ud=20150419000210|publisher=[[The Korea Herald]]|last1=Jung|first1=Won-ho|website=Korea Herald|language=en-US|date=April 19, 2015|accessdate=March 9, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Korean success|url=https://www.asiatvforum.com/News-and-Media/Insights-Magazine/directory/korean-success/|publisher=Asia TV Forum|last1=Mendoza|first1=Lunita|website=asiatvforum.com|language=en-US|date=February 27, 2017|accessdate=March 9, 2020}}</ref> It was distributed worldwide by CJ ENM and several television distributors, such as [[Endemol Shine Group]] and [[Fox Corporation]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Endemol, CJ E&M ink international partnership|url=https://realscreen.com/2016/04/27/endemol-cj-em-ink-international-partnership/|publisher=[[Realscreen]]|last1=Alcinii|first1=Daniele|website=realscreen.com|language=en-US|date=April 27, 2016|accessdate=March 9, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Fox doubles down on Korean formats with CJ ENM singing format|url=https://tbivision.com/2020/02/07/fox-doubles-down-on-korean-formats-with-cj-enm-singing-format/|publisher=Television Business International|last1=Middleton|first1=Richard|website=tbivision.com|language=en-US|date=February 7, 2020|accessdate=March 9, 2020}}</ref>\n\nA [[Spin-off (television)|spin-off]] program, ''[[Hidden Voices (game show)|Gi\u1ecdng \u1ea3i gi\u1ecdng ai]]'' (also called ''Hidden Voices''), being also as part of a ICSYV franchise, which created the versus format that led into adopted to ICSYV counterparts.<ref>{{cite web|title=\"Ch\u1ebft c\u01b0\u1eddi\" v\u1edbi I Can See Your Voice phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Vi\u1ec7t|url=https://tinnhac.com/chet-cuoi-voi-i-can-see-your-voice-phien-ban-viet-90917.html|publisher=T\u00edn Nh\u1eafc |language=vi|website=tinnhac.com|date=November 8, 2016|accessdate=August 11, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Fan Kpop \u1edf nh\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng d\u1ecbch r\u1ea3nh rang n\u00ean 'c\u00e0y' ngay nh\u1eefng show \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00e0y! - Tiin|url=http://m.tiin.vn/chuyen-muc/nhac/khi-fan-kpop-o-nha-chong-dich-nen-cay-ngay-nhung-show-am-nhac-nay-vi-ban-se-khong-that-vong-dau.html|publisher=Tiin |language=vi|website=tiin.vn|date=April 11, 2020|accessdate=April 11, 2020}}</ref>\n\nThe ICSYV franchise have unique terms such as celebrity panelists (''SING-vestigators''<ref>{{cite web|title=Meet the SINGvestigators of I Can See Your Voice|url=https://entertainment.abs-cbn.com/tv/shows/icanseeyourvoice/videos/2017/09/13/01091417-meet-i-can-see-your-voice-singvestigators|publisher=ABS-CBN Entertainment |language=en-US|website=entertainment.abs-cbn.com|date=September 14, 2017|accessdate=March 9, 2020}}</ref>), mystery singers (''SEE-cret songers''<ref name=\"Terms1\">{{Cite web|url=http://entertainment.abs-cbn.com/tv/shows/icanseeyourvoice/Show-Updates/2017/09/13/24091317-mystery-music-game-show-i-can-see-your-voice-premieres-on-abs-cbn|title=Mystery music game show \"I Can See Your Voice\" premieres on ABS-CBN|publisher=[[ABS-CBN News]]|website=entertainment.abs-cbn.com |date=September 13, 2017 |accessdate=March 10, 2020}}</ref>), and the ''stage of truth''<ref name=\"Terms1\" /> (or other terms that depends on version).\n\n==Summary==\n<!---If you put season's broadcasting date there, use {{Start date}} for premiere, and {{End date}} for finale episode.\n\nTo avoid confusion, the TV channel of the ICSYV franchise is added with the designated country.--->\n\n;''Color key''\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n{{plainlist|\n* {{Color box|#9f9|border=darkgray}} Currently airing\n* {{Color box|#f99|border=darkgray}} Ceased to air\n* {{Color box|#ffff90|border=darkgray}} An upcoming show or season\n}}\n{{col-end}}\n\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; line-height:16px; width:100%;\"\n|-\n!rowspan=2 scope=row width=01%|Country\n!rowspan=2 scope=row width=01%|Local title\n!colspan=2 scope=row width=37%|Presenters\n!colspan=2 scope=row width=37%|Panelists\n!rowspan=2 scope=row width=01%|Network\n!rowspan=2 scope=row width=15%|Seasons\n|-\n!width=19.5%|Current\n!width=19.5%|Former\n!width=19.5%|Current\n!width=19.5%|Former\n|-{{no}}\n!{{BUL}}\n|'''''[[Peesh ili luzhesh]]'''''<br>{{small|[[:bg:\u041f\u0435\u0435\u0448 \u0438\u043b\u0438 \u043b\u044a\u0436\u0435\u0448|\u041f\u0435\u0435\u0448 \u0438\u043b\u0438 \u043b\u044a\u0436\u0435\u0448]]}}\n|{{N/A}}\n|{{plainlist|*{{ill|Maria Ignatova|bg|\u041c\u0430\u0440\u0438\u044f \u0418\u