ration of God\u2019s unfathomable direction of men\u2019s affairs).<ref name=\"Asad-Surah-Intro\" />\n\n|-\n| 13 || [[Ar-Ra'd|Ar-Ra'd]]\n| {{lang|ar|\u0671\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u0639\u0652\u062f}}<br/>{{transl|ar|ar-Ra\u02bfd}}\n| The Thunder || 43 (6) || Madinah  || 96 || 90 || Alif Lam Mim Ra || v. 13 <ref name=\"Asad-Surah-Intro\" /> ||\n* God\u2019s revelation, through his prophets, of certain fundamental moral truths, and the concequences of accepting or rejecting them.<ref name=\"Asad-Surah-Intro\" />\n\n|-\n| 14 || [[Ibrahim (sura)|Ibrahim]]\n|{{lang|ar|\u0625\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u064a\u0645}}<br/>{{transl|ar|\u02beIbr\u0101h\u012bm}}\n|[[Abraham]]|| 52 (7) || Makkah || 72 || 76 || Alif Lam Ra || v. 35-41 <ref name=\"Asad-Surah-Intro\" /> ||\n* The revelation of God\u2019s word to all mankind, destined to lead man from darkness to light.<ref name=\"Asad-Surah-Intro\" />\n\n|-\n| 15 || [[Al-Hijr]] \n|{{lang|ar|\u0671\u0644\u0652\u062d\u0650\u062c\u0652\u0631}}<br/>{{transl|ar|al-\u1e24ijr}}\n| The Rocky Tract, The Stoneland, The Rock City, Al-Hijr || 99 (6) || Makkah || 54 || 57 || Alif Lam Ra || v. 80 <ref name=\"Asad-Surah-Intro\" /> ||\n* God\u2019s guidance to man through revelation of the Qur'an, which will remain uncorrupted for all times. (v. 9) <ref name=\"Asad-Surah-Intro\" />\n\n|-\n| 16 || [[An-Nahl]] \n|{{lang|ar|\u0671\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0644}}<br/>{{transl|ar|an-Na\u1e25l}}\n| The Honey Bees, The Bee || 128 (16) || Makkah || 70 || 73 || || v. 68-69 <ref name=\"Asad-Surah-Intro\" /> ||\n* God\u2019s creativeness:<ref name=\"Asad-Surah-Intro\" /> \n** Manifested in the instincts of the bee.<ref name=\"Asad-Surah-Intro\" /> \n** Culmination: Guidance through his revealed word.<ref name=\"Asad-Surah-Intro\" />\n\n|-\n| 17 || [[Al-Isra|Al-Isra']]\n|{{lang|ar|\u0671\u0644\u0652\u0625\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0621}}<br/>{{transl|ar|al-\u02beIsr\u0101\u02be}}\n|[[Isra and Mi'raj|The Night Journ